{
  "stem": "9963.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I said to him, maybe these people will need me more than you need me, because you won't need me here.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I went with all the people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "When we came to the train, was wagons prepared.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Put in 110, 120 people in a wagon.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But before they put us into the train, we had to take off our clothes, only the pants-- our coat, our shirts, our shoes, our shoes, our socks, everything-- only left us in the pants.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they took our clothes back to they camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "When they took our clothes back to the camp, they recognize our clothes, so they thought that did to us the same thing what they did to the thousands of people before, where they shot them and burned them.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So a panic start.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So there were over there two mechanics that were fixing the cars for the Gestapo and for the SS.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they fixed themselves a car, and they ran way.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When the two ran away, they took all the 48 people, and they shot them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That goes to show you if I would be selfish, and I stay with them, I wouldn't be talking to you now.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I wasn't selfish, I went with [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They took us to Birkenau-Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On the road, we recognized where we were-- where we're going.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People started jumping from the train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I told them, you know, there's nothing where to jump.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, it is so many things to talk, but such a long time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When we came to Birkenau-Auschwitz--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It took us about [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a day and a night.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We came to Birkenau-Auschwitz-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] well, a little bit more, because we left late in the evening, and we came over there late at night.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
